rows.label: tlk42300011_05_msg0001
rows.name:
When Alst becomes peaceful, Rimurimu
is going to change jobs and become a salvager, mo.

rows.label: tlk42300011_05_msg0002
rows.name:
I was actually going to do it right away,
but Kebikebi stopped me... mo.

rows.label: tlk42300011_05_msg0003
rows.name:
It seems Kebikebi actually likes Rimurimu
quite a bit, mo.

rows.label: tlk42300011_05_msg0004
rows.name:
So Rimurimu okay with staying around
little while longer.
